speech.p:
That any Act of the present Session to make provision in connection with the enlargement of the European Communities to include the United Kingdom, together with (for certain purposes) the Channel Islands, the Isle of Man and Gibraltar, may include provision—



(a) for giving effect to any charge to taxation of those Communities, and for the imposition and alteration of customs duties by order of the Treasury;

(b) for the payment into the Consolidated Fund or National Loans Fund of sums received by any Minister of the Crown or government department.
